PART 2: Implement Strategies (20 min)
Your manager should support 3 strategies:
Strategy 1: Sliding Window

Keep only last N messages
When adding new message, drop oldest if over limit

Strategy 2: Summarization

After X messages, summarize oldest
Keep summary + recent messages
Requires client for summarization

Strategy 3: Importance

Mark messages with keywords as important
Keep important + recent
Keywords: ['error', 'problem', 'name', 'critical', 'important']

Each strategy should be implemented as:

Either: Separate methods in ConversationManager
Or: Separate classes that ConversationManager uses
Your choice!

