💡 DESIGN HINTS
Think about:

Strategy Pattern: How will you switch between strategies?

If/else in methods?
Separate strategy classes?
Strategy parameter checked each time?

Tool Use: How to detect if content has tool_use blocks?

Check type of content items?
Separate method vs auto-detect?

Summarization: Needs client - how to handle?

Store client in init?
Pass client to methods that need it?
Raise error if strategy needs client but not provided?

Error Handling: What if someone does:

Wrong strategy name?
Summarization without client?
Invalid message format?

